Author: RHOVIT
Title: [ANN][ICO] RHOVIT - Content Monetization Marketplace
Body: Our project is much more geared towards helping content providers monetize their material. Initially we are not trying to use blockchain as a way to claim ownership, though it may be something we integrate in the future.  The circular economy that's based on both a crypto and virtual currency, and the way in which we use the Rbit Token to fuel and regenerate constant value for the community is what we believe sets the platform apart.

Title: [ANN][ICO] RHOVIT - Content Monetization Marketplace

Author: irishboxer
Title: [ANN][ICO] RHOVIT - Content Monetization Marketplace
Body: You say it's a hybrid platform. Can you explain why you chose not to build the whole thing on blockchain? And what aspects of the site are specifically blockchain based?

Author: RHOVIT
Title: [ANN][ICO] RHOVIT - Content Monetization Marketplace
Body: Sure. All media will be stored on the cloud. Blockchain is used to run all the transactions on the site i.e purchasing films, music - watching promoted ads or sharing promoted posts. These transactions are what is used to "mine" the Rbits on the platform which then get distributed out to the community.
